i, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px;\">(518) 729-9887</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"card-text\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 1rem; color: #212529; font-family: -apple-system, system-ui, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px;\">Posted by: Sydney Luke</p>', 661582760, 32, '2019-02-02 21:54:42'),
('Volunteering Opportunity', 'Volunteering Opportunity', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Verdana\',sans-serif;\">Cadets,</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Verdana\',sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; word-spacing: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: \'Verdana\',sans-serif;\">We have been offered the opportunity to help work the career fair this coming <strong>Wednesday, 6th February</strong>. Some of the duties include,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 11.0pt; font-family: \'Verdana\',sans-serif; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;\">helping to distribute boxes as well as directing parking up at the Field House parking lot. The career fair is in need of people from <strong>0800 to 1700</strong>. This is a great opportunity for community outreach. If you are able and willing to give a few hours of your time, please click the read and understood button on this post so that I can pass interest on to the organizers.&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; widows: 2; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; word-spacing: 0px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.6667px;\">Very Respectfully,&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.6667px;\">&nbsp;</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.6667px;\">IVAN A. BERETVAS, C/Col, AFROTC</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.6667px;\">Commander</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.6667px;\">550th AFROTC Cadet Wing</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.6667px;\">bereti@rpi.edu</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14.6667px;\">(518) 542-7984</span></span></p>', 661429225, 33, '2019-02-02 22:46:52'),
('LLAB 3', 'LLAB 3', '<p>Cadets,</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Operation:&nbsp; Free Fallin\'</p>\r\n<p>Date:&nbsp; 5 February 2019</p>\r\n<p>Location:&nbsp; Empire State Aeroscience Museum</p>\r\n<p>Time:&nbsp; 0750</p>\r\n<p>UOD:&nbsp; The Uniform of the Day (UOD) will be the Airman Battle Uniform (ABU).&nbsp; Cadets who have not been issued ABUs will wear Black Polo and Khakis (BPaK).</p>\r\n<p>OPORD:&nbsp; OPORD to come</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Very Respectfully,</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>COLLIN T. RECORE, C/3C, AFROTC</p>\r\n<p>Bravo Flight</p>\r\n<p>550th AFROTC Training Squadron</p>\r\n<p>recorc@rpi.edu</p>\r\n<p>(315) 720-9875</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 661502656, 34, '2019-02-03 22:53:18');
